## ***i-The Hearth (Universal Foundations): (Ch1)***
The hearth, also known as the Tower's core, is where the Ancient Laws are writen on the bedrock upon which all magical engineering is built. Regardless of which CodeTower a wizard enters, the universal standards of the Hearth remain constant. It is the interface between the wizard's intent and the machine's reality.

